ARM: dts: sun8i: Add BananaPI M2-Magic DTS

The Bananapi M2-Magic is a board with an A33, a USB host and USB OTG
connectors, and 8GB eMMC, an AP6212 WiFi/Bluetooth chip and connectors for
DSI, CSI and GPIOs.

